================================================================================
                              THE BEGINNING
================================================================================

This journey began with a simple question: What if we could prevent errors
before they happen? Not just catch them at runtime, but anticipate them at
the pattern level - catching the very assumptions and cascades that lead
to catastrophic failures.

The kernel is not just another component. It is the collective intelligence
of 80+ reflections, distilled into a pattern matching engine that watches
for the fatal assumptions and bug cascades that have haunted software
development for decades.

